%20will%20do%20so%20too%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20a%20clarification%20is%20this%2C%20coming%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20is%20outraged%20over%20the%20way%20your%20Home%20Minister%20insulted%20Baba%20Saheb%20in%20Parliament.%20And%20your%20statement%20has%20sprinkled%20salt%20on%20the%20wound.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20remarks%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20election%20and%20the%20AAP%20would%20be%20looking%20to%20corner%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20on%20this%20issue.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20had%20hit%20out%20at%20Amit%20Shah%20over%20his%20remarks.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAmit%20Shah%20ji%2C%20Baba%20Saheb%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20god%20for%20every%20child%20in%20this%20country.%20We%20don't%20know%20about%20heaven%2C%20but%20if%20Baba%20Saheb's%20Constitution%20were%20not%20there%2C%20you%20would%20not%20let%20the%20oppressed%20and%20Dalits%20live%20on%20earth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20AAP%20protest%20later%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20reiterated%20that%20BR%20Ambedkar%20is%20god%20for%20Dalits.%20%26quot%3BI%20consider%20Ambedkar%20my%20idol.%20Not%20just%20me%2C%20my%20party%20too.%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20hurt%20our%20sentiments.%20The%20way%20the%20PM%20has%20come%20to%20Amit%20Shah's%20defence%20shows%20it%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20BJP.%20BJP%20supporters%20must%20choose%20if%20they%20are%20with%20BJP%20or%20with%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20demanded%20strict%20action%20against%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20said%20AAP%20would%20take%20this%20issue%20to%20every%20home%20in%20Delhi%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20election%20due%20in%20February.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20the%20BJP's%20firefight%20amid%20the%20Opposition's%20all-out%20offensive%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%20the%20people%20have%20seen%20how%20the%20Congress%20has%20tried%20%26quot%3Bevery%20possible%20trick%26quot%3B%20to%20obliterate%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20legacy%20and%20humiliate%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20six-point%20thread%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Brotten%20ecosystem%26quot%3B%20were%20%26quot%3Bgravely%20mistaken%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20thought%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20lies%26quot%3B%20could%20hide%20their%20insult%20of%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20rotten%20ecosystem%20think%20their%20malicious%20lies%20can%20hide%20their%20misdeeds%20of%20several%20years%2C%20especially%20their%20insult%20towards%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%2C%20they%20are%20gravely%20mistaken!%20The%20people%20of%20India%20have%20seen%20time%20and%20again%20how%20one%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20one%20dynasty%2C%20has%20indulged%20in%20every%20possible%20dirty%20trick%20to%20obliterate%20the%20legacy%20of%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20and%20humiliate%20the%20SC%2FST%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20video%20of%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20Home%20Minister%20had%20%26quot%3Bexposed%20the%20Congress'%20dark%20history%20of%20insulting%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20and%20ignoring%20the%20SC%2FST%20Communities%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20clearly%20stung%20and%20stunned%20by%20the%20facts%20he%20presented%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20are%20now%20indulging%20in%20theatrics!%20Sadly%2C%20for%20them%2C%20people%20know%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20his%20government%20has%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20fulfill%20the%20vision%20of%20Dr%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%2C%20our%20respect%20and%20reverence%20is%20absolute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah's%20remarks%2C%20which%20are%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20row%2C%20were%20made%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20yesterday%20during%20the%20debate%20to%20mark%2075%20years%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20a%20fashion%20to%20say%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar'.%20If%20they%20took%20God's%20name%20so%20many%20times%2C%20they%20would%20have%20got%20a%20place%20in%20heaven%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20his%20name%20100%20times%20more%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20say%20what%20are%20your%20sentiments%20about%20him.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20BR%20Ambedkar%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20following%20his%20disagreement%20with%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20Mr%20Shah%20of%20insulting%20the%20Dalit%20icon.%20When%20the%20Parliament%20met%20today%2C%20MPs%20from%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20held%20photos%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%20and%20staged%20a%20protest.%20While%20BJP%20leaders%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20circulating%20a%20short%20video%20clip%20that%20did%20not%20show%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20how%20the%20Congress%20allegedly%20sidelined%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20Opposition%20leaders%20stepped%20up%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20demanded%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734520260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F2k92sg2_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_11_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-amit-shah-arvind-kejriwal-sprinkling-salt-on-wound-arvind-kejriwal-on-pms-post-amid-ambedkar-row-7276380%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20amid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20