20(out)%20anybody.%20We%20will%20make%20sure%20the%20money...%20which%20has%20to%20go%20back%20to%20banks...%20will%20go%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister's%20staunch%20defence%20of%20the%20federal%20agency%20follows%20question%20marks%20last%20week%20over%20its%20conviction%20rate%3B%20that%20low%20figure%20-%20less%20than%20five%20per%20cent%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20-%20provided%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20with%20ammunition%20to%20attack%20the%20government%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20asked%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Mr%20Surjewala%20was%20told%20the%20ED%20had%20filed%20over%20900%20cases%20under%20the%20strict%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20or%20PMLA%2C%20from%202019%20to%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%20only%2042%2C%20or%204.6%20per%20cent%2C%20have%20resulted%20in%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20claimed%2C%20was%20proof%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20%26quot%3Bwitch%20hunt%26quot%3B%20against%20opposition%20leaders%3B%20the%20opposition%20has%20routinely%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20federal%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED%20to%20file%20false%20charges%20against%20rival%20parties%20and%20politicians%20to%20silence%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20conviction%20rate%20was%20also%20flagged%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20August%3B%20the%20top%20court%20reprimanded%20the%20ED%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20(the%20agency)%20needs%20to%20look%20at%20the%20quality%20of%20prosecution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20regard%20to%20tracking%20down%20and%20bringing%20back%20'black%20money'%2C%20or%20funds%20illegally%20acquired%20and%20parked%20abroad%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20Black%20Money%20Act%20(2015)%20has%20had%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20taxpayers%20and%20Indian%20citizens%20disclosing%20foreign%2