0Ambedkar%2C%20they%20are%20gravely%20mistaken!%20The%20people%20of%20India%20have%20seen%20time%20and%20again%20how%20one%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20one%20dynasty%2C%20has%20indulged%20in%20every%20possible%20dirty%20trick%20to%20obliterate%20the%20legacy%20of%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20and%20humiliate%20the%20SC%2FST%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIf%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20rotten%20ecosystem%20think%20their%20malicious%20lies%20can%20hide%20their%20misdeeds%20of%20several%20years%2C%20especially%20their%20insult%20towards%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%2C%20they%20are%20gravely%20mistaken!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20people%20of%20India%20have%20seen%20time%20and%20again%20how%20one%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20one%20dynasty%2C%20has%20indulged%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1869283020902993973%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20remarks%20come%20amid%20a%20massive%20protest%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20Opposition%20over%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20remarks%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20House%20during%20the%20debate%20to%20mark%2075%20years%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20taking%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20name%20had%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bfashion%26quot%3B%20now.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20a%20fashion%20to%20say%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar'.%20If%20they%20took%20God's%20name%20so%20many%20times%2C%20they%20would%20have%20got%20a%20place%20in%20heaven%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20his%20name%20100%20times%20more%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20say%20what%20are%20your%20sentiments%20about%20him.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20BR%20Ambedkar%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20following%20his%20disagreement%20with%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row%2C%20with%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20accusing%20Mr%20Shah%20of%20insulting%20the%20Dalit%20icon.%20When%20the%20Parliament%20met%20today%2C%20MPs%20from%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20held%20photos%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%20and%20staged%20a%20protest.%20While%20BJP%20leaders%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20circulating%20a%20short%20video%20clip%20that%20did%20not%20show%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20how%20the%20Congress%20allegedly%20sidelined%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20Opposition%20leaders%20stepped%20up%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20demanded%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Opposition%20tried%20to%20shape%20the%20narrative%20and%20corner%20the%20government%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20swung%20into%20action%20to%20counter%20the%20Opposition's%20attack%20that%20could%20potentially%20have%20a%20massive%20perception%20impact%20among%20backward%20communities.%20Mr%20Shah%20met%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20his%20residence%20amid%20the%20spiralling%20row.%C2%A0The%20Prime%20Minister%20added%20in%20his%20post%20that%20the%20list%20of%20the%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bsins%26quot%3B%20towards%20BR%20Ambedkar%20includes%3A%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20him%20defeated%20in%20elections%20not%20once%20but%20twice%2C%20Pandit%20Nehru%20campaigning%20against%20him%20and%20making%20his%20loss%20a%20prestige%20issue%2C%20denying%20him%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20denying%20his%20portrait%20a%20place%20of%20pride%20in%20Parliament's%20Central%20Hall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20can%20try%20as%20they%20want%20but%20they%20can't%20deny%20that%20the%20worst%20massacres%20against%20SC%2FST%20Communities%20have%20happened%20under%20their%20regimes.%20For%20years%2C%20they%20sat%20in%20power%20but%20did%20nothing%20substantive%20to%20empower%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20video%20of%20Mr%20Shah's%20remarks%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20Home%20Minister%20had%20%26quot%3Bexposed%20the%20Congress'%20dark%20history%20of%20insulting%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20and%20ignoring%20the%20SC%2FST%20Communities%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20clearly%20stung%20and%20stunned%20by%20the%20facts%20he%20presented%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20are%20now%20indulging%20in%20theatrics!%20Sadly%2C%20for%20them%2C%20people%20know%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20his%20government%20has%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20fulfill%20the%20vision%20of%20Dr%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%2C%20our%20respect%20and%20reverence%20is%20absolute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20insulting%20BR%20Ambedkar%20during%20and%20after%20his%20lifetime.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20under%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20honoured%20every%20place%20linked%20to%20Baba%20Saheb.%20This%20is%20what%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20put%20forward%20yesterday%20with%20proof.%20The%20Congress%20has%20resorted%20to%20nasty%20politics%20to%20hide%20this%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20countered%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%2C%20an%20X%20account%20called%20Modi%20Archive%2C%20which%20shares%20trivia%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20political%20journey%2C%20shared%20his%20old%20pictures%20offering%20tribute%20to%20Dr%20Ambedkar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narend