%E2%80%99t%20one%20to%20get%20bogged%20down.%20Instead%20of%20feeling%20discouraged%2C%20he%20used%20the%20feedback%20as%20motivation%20to%20improve%20his%20presentation%20and%20communication%20skills.%20This%20approach%20resonated%20with%20his%20audience%2C%20who%20soon%20became%20a%20fan%20of%20his%20authenticity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinchen%E2%80%99s%20videos%2C%20showcasing%20his%20love%20for%20cooking%20and%20the%20unique%20flavours%20of%20his%20momos%2C%20quickly%20gained%20traction%20on%20social%20media.%20As%20the%20buzz%20around%20his%20shop%20grew%2C%20long%20queues%20of%20customers%20eager%20to%20relish%20his%20momos%20could%20be%20seen%20outside%20his%20shop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20has%20over%20four%20lakh%20followers%20and%20owns%20a%20restaurant%20where%20people%20line%20up%20for%20his%20iconic%20rose%20momos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20he%20even%20received%20appreciation%20for%20his%20work%20from%20Sikkim%20Chief%20Minister%20Prem%20Singh%20Tamang.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20imagined%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344409%2Ffomo-momo-food-truck-new-jersey-serves-tandoori-butter-garlic-momos-women-missed-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20for%20cooking%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewould%20take%20me%20this%20far.%20This%20moment%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20dreams%20do%20come%20true%20if%20you%20work%20hard%20and%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20This%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%2C%20and%20I%20am%20excited%20to%20see%20where%20this%20journey%20takes%20me%20next.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20continue%20to%20inspire%20each%20other%20and%20chase%20our%20dreams%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734510600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D389356%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%