20felt%20that%2C%20'if%20I'm%20not%20needed%20right%20now%20in%20the%20series%2C%20I'm%20better%20off.%20Saying%20goodbye%20to%20the%20game%2C%20but%20obviously%2C%20we've%20not%20been%20to%20Melbourne%20yet%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20sort%20of%20conditions%20we%20expect%20there%20and%20what%20sort%20of%20combination%2C%20but%20just%20keeping%20Ash%20in%20particularly%20in%20mind%2C%20giving%20him%20that%20respect%20that%20this%20if%20this%20is%20what%20he%20thinks%2C%20we%20should%20allow%20him%20to%20think%20that%20way%20and%20we%20should%20all%20stand%20by.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-olk-copy-source%3D%5C%22MessageBody%5C%22%3EThe%2038-year-old%20retires%20from%20the%20game%20as%20the%20second%20highest%20wicket-taker%20for%20India%20in%20Tests%20with%20537%20scalps%20in%20106%20games%2C%20placing%20him%20only%20behind%20the%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Anil%20Kumble%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F265-anil-kumble-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kumble%3C%2Fa%3E%20(619%20wickets)%20in%20the%20overall%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20limited-overs%20format%2C%20being%20part%20of%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%202013%20Champions%20Trophy-winning%20teams%20would%20count%20among%20the%20highlights%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20big%20match-winner%20for%20us.%20He%20is%20allowed%20to%20make%20those%20decisions%20on%20his%20own%2C%20and%20if%20it%20was%20now%2C%20so%20be%20it.%20He%20looks%20a%20very%20witty%20character%2C%20as%20you%20saw%20in%20his%20press%20conference.%20He%20is%20a%20very%20funny%20guy%2C%20there's%20no%20doubt%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20played%20cricket%20with%20Ash%20since%20under%2017%3B%20he%20was%20an%20opener%20batsman%20then%2C%20and%20then%20a%20few%20years%20later%2C%20we%20all%20disappeared%20and%20then%20suddenly%20I'm%20hearing%20news%20about%20Tamil%20Nadu%20R%20Ashwin%20taking%20five%20wic