3%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20much%20about%20avocados%20in%20my%20region%2C%20but%20after%20I%20distributed%20samples%2C%20they%20became%20curious.%20Slowly%2C%20the%20demand%20started%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20behind%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20his%20commitment%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386464%2Fcouples-organic-farming-business-sreshte-guntur-andhra-pradesh-turnover-90-lakh-per-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAvocados%20are%20a%20healthy%20fruit%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20them%20that%20way.%20Initially%2C%20I%20used%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%2C%20but%20after%20learning%20about%20organic%20farming%2C%20I%20changed%20my%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20cow%20dung%20manure%20and%20natural%20farming%20methods%20not%20only%20ensures%20the%20health%20of%20the%20plants%20but%20also%20appeals%20to%20consumers%20who%20are%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20organic%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESister%20Annie%2C%20an%20advocate%20of%20sustainable%20agriculture%2C%20has%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20his%20transformation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20visited%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20and%20observed%20his%20avocado%20cultivation%20practices.%20After%20recommending%20a%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20the%20results%20were%20remarkable.%20The%20yield%20improved%20significantly%2C%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20fruit%20enhanced%2C%20and%20they%20stayed%20fresh%20for%20a%20week%20without%20refrigeration%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%20significantly%20increased%20his%20profits%20by%20incorporating%20grafting%20techniques%20into%20his%20farming%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CGrafting%20helps%20extend%20the%20lifespan%20of%20the%20plants%2C%20which%20will%20benefit%20future%20generations%20of%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Today%2C%20Parmeshwar's%20farm%20houses%20300%20avocado%20trees%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-800x800.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-600x600.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-400x400.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-200x200.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.15.31-1_11zon-1734346242-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-389605%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20houses%20300%20avocado%20trees%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrafting%20involves%20joining%20the%20roots%20of%20one%20plant%20(known%20as%20rootstock)%20with%20the%20shoot%20or%20sapling%20of%20another%20(called%20the%20scion).%20He%20sources%20the%20rootstock%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20uses%20scions%20from%20his%20existing%20plants.%20This%20technique%20not%20only%20improves%20the%20health%20of%20the%20plants%20but%20also%20enhances%20their%20yield%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20These%20plants%20are%20expected%20to%20start%20fruiting%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20%E2%80%9CGrafting%20is%20a%20game-changer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20extends%20the%20lifespan%20of%20avocado%20plants%20and%20boosts%20their%20yield%20potential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%2C%20a%2062-year-old%20retired%20postal%20employee%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20supporting%20Parmeshwar%20by%20supplying%20avocado%20plants%20for%20his%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20come%20from%20a%20non-farming%20background%2C%20we%20both%20began%20this%20journey%20of%20avocado%20farming%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Parmeshwar%20visited%20Karnataka%20to%20learn%20about%20avocado%20cultivation%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20Kannada%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20met.%20I%20explained%20everything%20to%20him.%20His%20perseverance%20and%20dedication%20were%20clear%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20they%20helped%20him%20become%20a%20successful%20avocado%20farmer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20avocado%20saplings%20I%20planted%20have%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20thriving%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20now%20successfully%20harvesting%20avocados!%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20by%20example%3A%20Educating%20the%20next%20generation%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20avocado%20farming%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkable%20story%20of%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20sustainable%20practices.%20What%20started%20with%20just%2050%20saplings%20on%20a%20small%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20now%20blossomed%20into%20a%20thriving%201.75-acre%20farm%20%E2%80%94%20home%20to%20300%20avocado%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20harvested%20and%20sold%20around%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20avocados%2C%20earning%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%205-6%20lakh%20after%20selling%20each%20fruit%20at%20Rs%20200.%E2%80%9D%20He%20mentions%20that%20maintaining%20the%20farm%20costs%20him%20about%20Rs%2050%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20selling%20the%20fruit%2C%20he%20has%20also%20ventured%20into%20selling%20avocado%20saplings.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20sold%202%2C300%20saplings%20at%20Rs%20300%20each.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20made%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%204.6%20lakh%20from%20sapling%20sales.%20In%20total%2C%20his%20net%20profit%20for%20the%20year%202023%20was%20approximately%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201971px)%20100vw%2C%201971px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2